CONTENTS

This directory contains a Ruby version of an example from Apple's Sample Code library.

ORIGINAL EXAMPLE

The original example may be found here:
http://developer.apple.com/samplecode/RoundTransparentWindow/RoundTransparentWindow.html

NOTES

An article describing the conversion is available at http://www.rubycocoa.com/the-rubification-of-rtw.

